PN,31801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784404081
OL,3,CChildren as young as four using anti-
OL,4,Cageing skincare products
OL,6,FChildren are increasingly using
OL,7,Fpowerful ingredients intended for
OL,8,Fmature skin after watching skincare
OL,9,Fcontent on social media, ITV News'
OL,10,FSangita Lal and Sasha Kay report.
OL,12,FWords by ITV News producer Sasha Kay.
OL,14,FChildren as young as four are using
OL,15,Fanti-ageing skincare products designed
OL,16,Ffor adults, prompting dermatologists
OL,17,Fto call for warning labels and tougher
OL,18,Fscrutiny of how the products are
OL,19,Fmarketed to young people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784404081
OL,3,CChildren as young as four using anti-
OL,4,Cageing skincare products
OL,6,FThe British Association of
OL,7,FDermatologists (BAD) has said stronger
OL,8,Flabelling is needed on products that
OL,9,Fcontain ingredients unsuitable for
OL,10,Fchildren's skin, warning they can
OL,11,Fcause irritation, allergic reactions
OL,12,Fand damage to the skin barrier.
OL,14,FExperts say they are increasingly
OL,15,Fseeing children using powerful
OL,16,Fingredients intended for mature skin
OL,17,Fafter watching skincare content on
OL,18,Fsocial media.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784404081
OL,3,CChildren as young as four using anti-
OL,4,Cageing skincare products
OL,6,FThirteen-year-old Sienna thought she
OL,7,Fwas taking part in a harmless social
OL,8,Fmedia trend when she filmed herself
OL,9,Ftrying skincare with friends at a
OL,10,F'pamper party'.
OL,12,FAfter watching online videos promoting
OL,13,Fanti-ageing routines, she unknowingly
OL,14,Fused products formulated and tested
OL,15,Ffor adult skin.
OL,17,FAs a result, she suffered a severe
OL,18,Freaction that left her with a swollen
OL,19,Frash that took months to heal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784404081
OL,3,CChildren as young as four using anti-
OL,4,Cageing skincare products
OL,6,F"The skin was peeling, very itchy,"
OL,7,Fshe said.
OL,9,FSienna is part of a growing social
OL,10,Fmedia trend in which children post
OL,11,Felaborate skincare routines featuring
OL,12,Fproducts designed to prevent wrinkles
OL,13,Fand signs of ageing.
OL,15,FVideos tagged "Get Ready With Me" show
OL,16,Fyoung girls applying serums, retinol,
OL,17,Fand acids commonly marketed to adults.
OL,18,FThey copy adult influencers who
OL,19,Fpromote anti-ageing cosmetics online.
OL,26,@nD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784404081
OL,3,CChildren as young as four using anti-
OL,4,Cageing skincare products
OL,6,FOur investigation found children as
OL,7,Fyoung as four using these products
OL,8,Fonline.
OL,10,FResearch from the Cosmetic, Toiletry
OL,11,Fand Perfumery Association (CTPA) shows
OL,12,F61% of parents say their child aged
OL,13,Fbetween eight and 14 uses skincare
OL,14,Fproducts. Of those, one in ten are
OL,15,Fusing anti-ageing creams or serums.
OL,17,FDermatologist warning
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784404081
OL,3,CChildren as young as four using anti-
OL,4,Cageing skincare products
OL,6,FThe BAD wants clearer product
OL,7,Flabelling, including warnings when
OL,8,Fproducts are unsuitable for children
OL,9,Fand information on risks such as
OL,10,Firritation, allergic reactions and
OL,11,Flonger-term skin damage.
OL,13,FPaediatric and Adolescent
OL,14,FDermatologist Dr Tess McPherson says
OL,15,Fexperts are seeing marketing
OL,16,Fstrategies for anti-ageing products
OL,17,Faimed at children as young as four or
OL,18,Ffive.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784404081
OL,3,CChildren as young as four using anti-
OL,4,Cageing skincare products
OL,6,F"We're calling for a light to be shone
OL,7,Fon some of these marketing techniques,
OL,8,Fwhich are preying on vulnerable
OL,9,Fchildren," Dr McPherson said.
OL,11,F"We want product information to have
OL,12,Fmuch clearer information, when it's
OL,13,Fnot suitable for children and to
OL,14,Finclude the risks of skin irritation,
OL,15,Fskin allergy and the longer term risks
OL,16,Fto children's well-being.
OL,18,F"Children shouldn't be worrying about
OL,19,Fold skin when they're as young as five
OL,20,For six, which feels quite dystopian."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784404081
OL,3,CChildren as young as four using anti-
OL,4,Cageing skincare products
OL,6,FSienna backs up this call from the
OL,7,FBAD: "What needs to change is the
OL,8,Fpackaging and labels on things. So
OL,9,Fdon't make it look like children are
OL,10,Fgonna buy it - that's not okay.
OL,12,F"It's supposed to be for older women
OL,13,Fand older men, but you're making it
OL,14,Flook like a children's brand and I
OL,15,Fdon't think that's okay."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784404081
OL,3,CChildren as young as four using anti-
OL,4,Cageing skincare products
OL,6,FHeidi Katona, influencer and daughter
OL,7,Fof Kerry Katona, said she has seen the
OL,8,Ftrend affect her own family and
OL,9,Fbelieves many parents do not realise
OL,10,Fthat some of the products contain
OL,11,Fpowerful anti-ageing ingredients.
OL,13,FShe told ITV News her younger sister
OL,14,Fbegan using skincare aged about nine,
OL,15,Fincluding products containing retinol
OL,16,Fand glycolic acid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784404081
OL,3,CChildren as young as four using anti-
OL,4,Cageing skincare products
OL,6,F"All these really harsh chemicals are
OL,7,Factually damaging their skin barrier
OL,8,Fbecause their skin is so soft and so
OL,9,Fgentle, they don't need it. It
OL,10,Factually really upsets me," Heidi said.
OL,12,FHeidi believes there is a lack of
OL,13,F"education" and transparency about the
OL,14,Frisks to children.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784404081
OL,3,CChildren as young as four using anti-
OL,4,Cageing skincare products
OL,6,F"I don't think people realise what
OL,7,Fthey're putting on their faces. I
OL,8,Fthink maybe if there was a bit more
OL,9,Feducation behind it or brands were
OL,10,Factually telling you you're putting
OL,11,Fanti-ageing products on a five-year-
OL,12,Fold, it's wrong," she continued.
OL,14,FHeidi says she thinks the "bright
OL,15,Fcolours and really fun designs" of
OL,16,Fskincare products target children.
OL,18,F"There should be a massive change in
OL,19,Fadvertising and marketing," she said.
OL,26,@vD@[OUwD@_O]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784404081
OL,3,CChildren as young as four using anti-
OL,4,Cageing skincare products
OL,6,F"That's childish designs. You are
OL,7,Faiming that towards children. But the
OL,8,Fproducts, the product itself, the
OL,9,Fingredients made from it aren't for
OL,10,Fchildren.
OL,12,F"I also want better regulations.
OL,13,FWarning labels: 'This isn't for kids'."
OL,15,FSienna's mum, Marie, agreed that the
OL,16,Fdesigns are misleading. She has
OL,17,Fpreviously bought skincare products,
OL,18,Fwhich she believed were harmless as
OL,19,Fthey appeared child-friendly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784404081
OL,3,CChildren as young as four using anti-
OL,4,Cageing skincare products
OL,6,F"I didn't know then about retinol and
OL,7,Facid and all these kinds of things.
OL,8,FIt's like, well, it looks child-
OL,9,Ffriendly and it looks okay," Marie
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"Sienna's seeing everyone using it, so
OL,13,Fshe can have it because there are
OL,14,Fworse things that you could want us to
OL,15,Fbuy. But there's way more to it than
OL,16,Fjust buying your daughter some
OL,17,Fskincare."
OL,19,FBrands targeting young girls
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784404081
OL,3,CChildren as young as four using anti-
OL,4,Cageing skincare products
OL,6,FSince her daughter's videos gained
OL,7,Fattention online, Sienna's mother says
OL,8,Fskincare companies have approached her
OL,9,Fwith collaboration deals.
OL,11,F"We're getting emails from full-on
OL,12,FKorean skincare brands," she said.
OL,14,F"I'm looking at these products and
OL,15,Fthinking: this is the kind of stuff
OL,16,FI'd use as a 45-year-old."
OL,18,FSienna felt she didn't know the risks
OL,19,Fwhen these brands approached her.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31815
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784404081
OL,3,CChildren as young as four using anti-
OL,4,Cageing skincare products
OL,6,F"I've been asked by quite a lot of
OL,7,Fbrands," she said.
OL,9,F"It's really worrying sometimes
OL,10,Fbecause it's like: what if I had gone
OL,11,Fwith that and then used it on my skin?
OL,12,FIt would have been terrible."
OL,14,FHeidi thinks that what Sienna's gone
OL,15,Fthrough with brands is "honestly
OL,16,Fdisgusting".
OL,18,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31816
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784404081
OL,3,CChildren as young as four using anti-
OL,4,Cageing skincare products
OL,6,F"You're coming at the most vulnerable.
OL,7,FYou're targeting them, you're sending
OL,8,Fthem these products to promote and
OL,9,Fthey're not actually even sure what's
OL,10,Fin them. I think it's wrong."
OL,12,FThe Advertising Standards Authority
OL,13,F(ASA) said: "At this point, we haven't
OL,14,Fseen evidence of inappropriate
OL,15,Fadvertising of skincare products to
OL,16,Fchildren, but it's an area we're
OL,17,Fcontinuing to explore.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31817
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784404081
OL,3,CChildren as young as four using anti-
OL,4,Cageing skincare products
OL,6,F"In terms of our rules, advertisers
OL,7,Fhave a responsibility to ensure that
OL,8,Ftheir ads are socially responsible.
OL,9,FAds mustn't exploit children's
OL,10,Finexperience or vulnerability or
OL,11,Finclude anything that could cause them
OL,12,Fphysical, mental or moral harm.
OL,14,F"Ultimately, the protection of
OL,15,Fchildren sits at the heart of our work
OL,16,Fand if we do see evidence of
OL,17,Fpotentially harmful ads then we won't
OL,18,Fhesitate to take action."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31818
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784404081
OL,3,CChildren as young as four using anti-
OL,4,Cageing skincare products
OL,6,FFor advice and support for parents and
OL,7,Fchildren, the SkinCare Simplified
OL,8,FGuide sets out which ingredients to
OL,9,Favoid and how to care for young skin.
OL,11,FOn its website, the CTPA, a trade
OL,12,Fassociation representing producers,
OL,13,Fsellers and distributors of cosmetics
OL,14,Fin the UK, says that "anti-ageing
OL,15,Fproducts or complex routines should
OL,16,Fnot be used on young people's skin as
OL,17,Fthey are not designed for this
OL,18,Fpurpose".
OL,20,FTheir key advice is to stick to:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
